    • getObjectiveValue

      public double getObjectiveValue(boolean isParent, int individualId)
      Returns the objective value of the given individual

      Objective function : 

       f(s) = totalProfit, (if not exceed bin capacity)
      = min(profit) / (totalWeight - knapsackCapacity + 1), (otherwise)

      public int applyTournamentSelection()
      Tournament Selection

      Applies Tournament Selection to the parents and select the parent with the highest objective value in a random POPULATION_SIZE number of parents. Returns the index of that parent.

    • applyLocalSearchWithDoS

      public void applyLocalSearchWithDoS(int idChild) throws ExecutionControl.NotImplementedException
      Local Search with Depth of Search

      Applies the given child's Local Search method for Depth of Search times. For every Local Search algorithms except RMHC, if there is no improvement in a pass (which means there will not be any improvement in following passes), the process will be terminated to safe computational cost

      Throws:
      ExecutionControl.NotImplementedException

    • applyPopulationReplacement

      public void applyPopulationReplacement()
      Population replacement - Elitist replacement

      Replaces the current population with the offspring and replaces the worst offspring with the best solution if the best is not contained in the offspring
